&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;img&#x2F;2024&#x2F;app-on-flyio&#x2F;metrics_data_transfer_view.webp&quot; alt=&quot;Data tranfer&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
